𝐇𝐨𝐰 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐮𝐬 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐬

𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐮𝐬 is the data collector — it scrapes metrics from your servers, containers, or apps and stores them in a time-series database.

Key highlights:
🔹 Pull-based model — collects metrics via HTTP endpoints
🔹 Powerful PromQL — custom queries for deep analysis
🔹 Alertmanager integration — triggers alerts instantly
🔹 Highly scalable & open-source

Think of Prometheus as your metrics brain — always watching, recording, and learning from your systems.
